    "ailments_description": "The most common ailments you can heal with Zanthoxylum bungeanum are inflammation and fever reduction, which are effectively managed by its anti-inflammatory and antipyretic properties. Additionally, this plant is used to treat diarrhea and hypertension, as it has been shown to have a regulatory effect on gut motility and cardiovascular function. Zanthoxylum bungeanum also exhibits analgesic and anti-inflammatory properties, making it beneficial for arthritis and pain relief. Furthermore, its antidiabetic properties have been proven to help manage diabetes, while its antispasmodic and anti-inflammatory effects alleviate digestive issues and gastritis. The plant's antimicrobial and anti-inflammatory properties also make it effective in treating cough, rheumatism, asthma, gastroenteritis, infection, migraine, skin irritation, cold, gastrointestinal issues, and gout.",
