    "preparations_description": "The main herbal preparations of Zanthoxylum bungeanum are derived from its leaves, fruits and bark. Zanthoxylum tea is made from the leaves, which have been used in traditional medicine to treat fever, rheumatism, and skin conditions. Sichuan pepper oil, extracted from the seeds, is used to relieve pain, inflammation and digestive issues, due to its active compound hydroxy-alpha-sanshool. Sichuan pepper tea and Zanthoxylum bungeanum tea are also made from the leaves and seeds, which have been used to treat respiratory issues, such as bronchitis and asthma. Zanthoxylum bungeanum tincture is a concentrated liquid extract, often used to treat colds, flu and other viral infections, due to its antimicrobial properties.",
